{"tid":1420254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨尾叫人答玉石俱焚果個記者，你呀，過黎","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:53:33.000Z","uid":161430,"like":172,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbbb58d6ee837e9f6a0ba3457f80c65937051a0","tid":1420254,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">叫人答玉石俱焚果個記者，你呀</span><br />\n平時班高官唔答問題唔見你敢咁樣追問既<br />\n人地明明同記者咁合作<br />\n答曬絕大部分問題先搞到超曬時<br />\n你仲話人地唔想答<br />\n<br />\n呢d妓者同黑警一鳩樣<br />\n專係鐘意恰d普通市民<br />\n對住高官就敢怒不敢言甚至奶<br />\n<br />\n我不代表記者會果幾個人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我宜家喺度代表我自己屌柒你</span>"},{"pid":"6ae7193bdce8271280fd543a3c2dd175e13a362b","tid":1420254,"uid":161430,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"邊間報館架"},{"pid":"75b0124ae169ee13125af8b54e8cb9dc6056d1eb","tid":1420254,"uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"陣間四點去問啲警察不如"},{"pid":"d633f64c130b09eff39d8e6222e88cfd673294e7","tid":1420254,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"東施效顰"},{"pid":"3ecf4a4a0953161577264c4fe04621566ad95b7b","tid":1420254,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"下次唔該問返佢邊間傳媒"},{"pid":"0f43826fcffa5f3c02dab3c4e4f77242d58d10b7","tid":1420254,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:39.000Z","msg":"邊間咁低質"},{"pid":"9ce36d8503851f67794fef07d39fe72df4228b26","tid":1420254,"uid":259813,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"其實咁多次都冇聽過「玉石俱焚」四個字，係咪應該叫佢自己問林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f46644dde7a3f9f7d2305da5b94e5d7975592e","tid":1420254,"uid":134778,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f9266e57a06a0b9cb